   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 22, Mesore 4. Receive for the credit of Julius Theon and Julius Theon alias Tryphon, from Antiochos, bathman of the bath-house in Kerkemounis, of the rent that he owes for the 22nd year through Eutychos 36 drachmas. (2nd hd.) Receive 36 drachmas."</ab>
